abla } \cdot \mathbf { a }$ signaling pathway. We further demonstrated that NS3 competed with NEMO for bindingto LUBAC,which resulted in decreased LUBAC-mediated linear ubiquitylation of NEMO and thus inhibited theTNF- $\mathbf { 
